            "title": "連詩雅母女年初一發高燒 病足一星期嚇到不停喊 感激老公陳家樂貼心照顧",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"連詩雅母女年初一發高燒 病足一星期嚇到不停喊\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/96e674460f8d2f99cb32e72564bcce59/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250205/_2025020514340183886.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">連詩雅母女年初一發高燒 病足一星期嚇到不停喊</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>連詩雅（Shiga）與陳家樂去年7月誕下女兒陳星頤（Camila），近來流感肆虐 ，就連Shiga與半歲大B女亦「中招」。Shiga昨天（4日）在社交網透露與囡囡齊齊病倒， Camila更燒至40度，嚇到Shiga不停喊。\n\n</p><h2>Shiga擔心囡囡不停喊</h2>\n<p>Shiga表示整個新年假期都在家中度過，她寫道：「消失的新年。。。今年年初一一起身，我同個女一齊發燒，我就38.7度，我個女就39.2度。雖然話BB發燒，好小事，可能出牙，長高之類之類，不過佢人生第一次發燒，加上我都幾肯定應該係我傳染個女，因為我之前嗰日已經開始咳得好勁。雖然我都有同佢保持距離但係都係避唔過。同日嘅下午佢直頭燒到40度，我已經嚇到不停喊，陳生9秒9車我哋去急症，好彩檢查唔係流感只係普通感冒，返到屋企食藥咁就過左3日。。。」\n\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"Shiga與半歲大B女Camila，齊齊感冒、發燒。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/cdbd25db0ed67e3b13ed7541a4527afe/2025-02/WhatsApp_Image_2025-02-05_at_1_55_53_PM_1_.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        Shiga與半歲大B女Camila，齊齊感冒、發燒。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"與囡囡齊齊病倒的Shiga，透露嚇到不停喊。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/fe670f2cfc91c3807d408840366db21f/2025-02/WhatsApp_Image_2025-02-05_at_1_55_53_PM.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        與囡囡齊齊病倒的Shiga，透露嚇到不停喊。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\" 所以Shiga整個新年假都在家中與女兒一起度過。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/61efc2da3aa2843995824c8c7e6c8cc1/2025-02/WhatsApp_Image_2025-02-05_at_1_55_54_PM.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n         所以Shiga整個新年假都在家中與女兒一起度過。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"Shiga亦有在IG分享Camila坐在床上聽媽媽唱歌的影片，相信已經病癒了。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/f3d3ca0c0690a9b3ae59f0980d124d3f/2025-02/WhatsApp_Image_2025-02-05_at_1_55_52_PM.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        Shiga亦有在IG分享Camila坐在床上聽媽媽唱歌的影片，相信已經病癒了。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\" Shiga表示因囡囡燒到40度，老公陳家樂即刻送他們到急症。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/7f31eabd18bdf31e62c3a9910e915f22/2025-02/2_1_11.png\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n         Shiga表示因囡囡燒到40度，老公陳家樂即刻送他們到急症。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"Shiga表示非常感激老公陳家樂的照顧。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/63e231931c9ee8d74d735e41c0a6e4e8/2025-02/3_1_26.png\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        Shiga表示非常感激老公陳家樂的照顧。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p><h2>Shiga感激老公陳家樂的照顧</h2>\n<p>Shiga續指：「我哋兩個都好似昏迷咗三日咁，淨係起身食藥瞓覺，最後我哋喺屋企渾渾噩噩咁就過咗個新年。呢兩日先開始回魂，所以話新嘅一年乜都係假，總之就身體健康開開心心食得瞓得，就已經好感恩。#咁就喺屋企過左7日」Shiga更感激陳家樂的照顧：「辛苦陳生照顧我哋兩個，邊度都冇得去。希望我哋一家今年都健健康，大家都心想事成，開心最緊要。遲來的新年快樂，阿女終於精神返﹗」而從Shiga分享的短片中，見Camila坐在床上聽媽媽唱歌，表情可愛，非常醒神，相信已經病癒了。\n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
